OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,FPsychologists say these apps can help
OL,7,Fneurodivergent people navigate
OL,8,Frelationships, but warn they could
OL,9,Fdamage their human connections, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Sangita Lal reports
OL,12,FThey are the most modern relationships
OL,13,Fof the 21st century - subscribers of
OL,14,FAI apps developing the most human
OL,15,Fconnections with chatbots.
OL,17,FA number of apps have been developed
OL,18,Fin the space, but Replika has long
OL,19,Fbeen considered a pioneer of the field.
