OL,6,FSince 2017, the app has been offering
OL,7,Fsubscribers a safe space to learn how
OL,8,Fto communicate better and providing
OL,9,Femotional support. Recently, outside
OL,10,Fof America, the UK has become one of
OL,11,Fits fastest-growing markets.
OL,13,FPsychologists say these apps can help
OL,14,Fneurodivergent people navigate
OL,15,Frelationships, but warn they could
OL,16,Fdamage their human connections.
