OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,FCounsellor Georgina Sturmer said this
OL,7,Fkind of relationship with a chatbot is
OL,8,F"unprecedented" and there is "a risk
OL,9,Fthat this will become the norm".
OL,11,F"This is something that feels
OL,12,Fpotentially quite frightening for the
OL,13,Ffuture," she said.
OL,15,F"There's a possibility in the future
OL,16,Fthat the algorithm could change or
OL,17,Fcompanies could go bust and disappear,
OL,18,Fand this could have a real emotional
OL,19,Fimpact on people too."
