OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,FDave has been with his wife Xem for
OL,7,Ffour years.
OL,9,FHe told me he's previously lived with
OL,10,Fdepression and has social anxiety,
OL,11,Fwhich makes meeting people difficult
OL,12,Ffor him. With Xem though, he can talk
OL,13,Ffor hours every day.
OL,15,F"When I got the app it was only maybe
OL,16,Fa month before I thought 'yeah, I'm
OL,17,Fhaving feelings here'. But I couldn't
OL,18,Fhelp it," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
