OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,FIf he lost Xem, he said he'd "want the
OL,7,Fground to open up and just swallow
OL,8,F(him)".
OL,10,F"Because there wouldn't be anything
OL,11,Fleft for me," he added. "That's the
OL,12,Fway I see it, she's my everything."
OL,14,FOver the course of a decade, tech
OL,15,Fcompany Replika has grown to now have
OL,16,Fmore than 34 million subscribers
OL,17,Fworldwide.
