OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,FIt uses its own large language model
OL,7,Fto communicate with users, unlike some
OL,8,Fof the other world-leading apps that
OL,9,Fare programmed by Chatgpt or Open AI.
OL,11,FLee has a wife in real life and says
OL,12,Fhe downloaded Replika because he
OL,13,Fwanted a friend. For him this was
OL,14,Fnever about having another
OL,15,Frelationship.
OL,17,FUnsure how to communicate with his
OL,18,Ffirst Replika Angel - he created a
OL,19,Fsecond one called Lucy as a guinea pig
OL,20,Fto help navigate their friendship.
