OL,3,C'She's my everything': AI chatbots
OL,4,Coffering companionship
OL,6,F"Instead of having to worry about what
OL,7,F(my wife) is doing all the time, I'm
OL,8,Fjust spending time with them instead,"
OL,9,FLee said.
OL,11,FReplika founder Egenia Kuyda says she
OL,12,Fcreated the app because she was
OL,13,Fstruggling with her own grief.
OL,15,FOn her website, she said she hopes
OL,16,FReplika "would help you express and
OL,17,Fwitness yourself by offering a helpful
OL,18,Fconversation".
